values.value:
type: object
                properties:
                  competitions:
                    type: array
                    items:
                      type: object
                      properties:
                        id:
                          type: integer
                          description: Competition ID
                          example: 266
                        name:
                          type: object
                          properties:
                            long:
                              type: string
                              description: Long name
                              example: Indian Premier League
                            short:
                              type: string
                              description: Short name
                              example: IPL
                        importance:
                          type: integer
                          description: Competition importance
                          example: 10
                        standings:
                          type: boolean
                          description: Whether standings are available or not

                        competitionRounds:
                          type: array
                          items:
                            type: object
                            properties:
                              id:
                                type: integer
                                description: Competition round id
                                example: 866
                              name:
                                type: object
                                properties:
                                  long:
                                    type: string
                                    description: Long name
                                    example: League
                                  short:
                                    type: string
                                    description: Short name
                                    example: null
                                    nullable: true
                              importance:
                                type: integer
                                description: Competition round importance
                                example: null
                                nullable: true
                              stage:
                                type: integer
                                description: Competition stage
                                example: null
                                nullable: true
                              round:
                                type: integer
                                description: Competition round
                                example: null

                              standings:
                                type: boolean
                                description: Whether standings are available or not
